just cold, if you're not like,

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:34.410
you know, a taiko nut
the way Mark and I are.

00:07:34.410 --> 00:07:37.100
You know, you're probably
just thinking, you know, whoa,

00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:39.110
these guys are like in
really good shape; right?

00:07:39.110 --> 00:07:40.410
They are totally.

00:07:40.410 --> 00:07:42.670
They have like zero
