00:45:34.650 --> 00:45:38.950
the Smithsonian's
festival, Folklife Festival.

00:45:38.950 --> 00:45:41.820
Mark and I were part
of, for a week we were

00:45:41.820 --> 00:45:43.720
on the mall playing this
a couple times a day.

00:45:43.720 --> 00:45:45.730
It was a great experience.

00:45:45.730 --> 00:45:47.890
I still, like had
such a great time.

00:45:47.890 --> 00:45:49.760
And it was so meaningful
for all of us.

00:45:49.760 --> 00:45:53.010
But this video is from a
few years before we all came

00:45:53.010 --> 00:45:54.310
