01:03:37.500 --> 01:03:39.710
If you're kind of
seeing patterns as sort

01:03:39.710 --> 01:03:44.150
of things develop over time?

01:03:44.150 --> 01:03:48.980
&gt;&gt; Dr. Deborah Wong: Just as you
