01:03:48.980 --> 01:03:51.500
and sustained ideas and values.

01:03:51.500 --> 01:03:55.340
But I also see a lot of
change at the same time, yeah.

01:03:55.340 --> 01:03:56.910
You know, not surprisingly;
right?

01:03:56.910 --> 01:03:58.790
Both are going on, yeah.

01:03:58.790 --> 01:04:00.740
I do think we're
at a tipping point

01:04:00.740 --> 01:04:03.740
in the greater taiko scene.

01:04:03.740 --> 01:04:05.740
I do think that the emphasis

01:04:05.740 --> 01:04:09.190
